Paul Childs is the second Lib Dem parliamentary candidate to reveal he is HIV positive . 
  He said he burst into tears when he was diagnosed with the virus in 2011 . 
  Mr Childs said he was infuriated by Ukip leader Nigel Farage's 'scaremongering' over foreigners with the condition . 
  He is running in the Liverpool Riverside seat in the election . 
  Adrian Hyyrylainen-Trett said he got the virus intentionally as he embarked on a path of self 'annihilation'